OL,3,CThree arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cthreats that closed schools in Cardiff
OL,6,FA 12-year-old boy from Birmingham is
OL,7,Fone of three arrested in connection
OL,8,Fwith threats made towards Cardiff
OL,9,Fsecondary schools in March.
OL,11,FTwo adults were also arrested by South
OL,12,FWales Police, a 44-year-old woman and
OL,13,Fa 47-year-old man, also from
OL,14,FBirmingham.
OL,16,FAll three were arrested on suspicion
OL,17,Fof Bomb Hoax contrary to Criminal Law
OL,18,FAct 1977.
