OL,3,CThree arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cthreats that closed schools in Cardiff
OL,6,FEastern High and Llanishen High closed
OL,7,Ffor two days after threats were
OL,8,Falleged to have been made anonymously
OL,9,Fto the police's online chat between 15
OL,10,FMarch and 18 March.
OL,12,FACC Thomas Williams from South Wales
OL,13,FPolice said: "We understand the
OL,14,Fconsiderable concern this incident has
OL,15,Fcaused parents and the community. We
OL,16,Ftake these reports extremely seriously
OL,17,Fand investigations are ongoing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
