OL,3,CThree arrested in connection with
OL,4,Cthreats that closed schools in Cardiff
OL,6,F"I would also like to reassure
OL,7,Ffamilies that there remains no
OL,8,Fevidence of any persons attending any
OL,9,Fof the schools involved posing a
OL,10,Fthreat. We continue working closely
OL,11,Fwith our partners and thank the
OL,12,Fschools, parents and the wider
OL,13,Fcommunity for their support and
OL,14,Funderstanding."
